Package sootup.core.inputlocation

Class DefaultSourceTypeSpecifier

java.lang.Object
sootup.core.inputlocation.DefaultSourceTypeSpecifier
All Implemented Interfaces:
SourceTypeSpecifier
public class DefaultSourceTypeSpecifier extends Object implements SourceTypeSpecifier
Implements a very basic version of SourceTypeSpecifier which tells the type of a class by checking if it is a language build-in class.
